### 4. ä½¿ç”¨ FastAPI é›†æˆ

```python
from fastapi import FastAPI
from fastai_agent import Fastai

app = FastAPI()
agent = Fastai([Project, Context])

@app.post("/query")
async def query(query: str):
    result = await agent.run(query)
    return {"result": result}
```

